<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">凑整除法，方法一，除数首位是“9”，其余各位大数字（6、7、8、9）较多时。在被除数首位上定商，下加除数的补数和商的乘积，补数在第几位，就在被除数相应位上加。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">6528÷96=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 6528÷96</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=6528÷(100-4)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=60+(528+240)÷(100-4)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=60+(768+8×4)÷100</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=60+8</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=68</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>